snippet.title: Savant Game Trailer
snippet.description:
Savant - Ascent is a game developed by D-Pad Studio, working with EDM artist Savant!

Get it:
+ Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/259530/
+ AppStore: https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/savant-ascent/id737368932?mt=8&uo=4
+ PlayStore: http://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.dpadstudio.SavantGame

Official website:
http://www.savantgame.com
http://www.dpadstudio.com

Soundtrack by Savant: http://www.savantofficial.com

Song in trailer: Kali 47 from Savant's album, Cult, which you can get here:
http://www.beatport.com/release/cult/1120189
